## 28. `menu_element`

**Module:** Public Menu
**Description:** A single freely-positioned object on a `menu_page` canvas: free text, an image, a decorative shape, or a product card linked live to the product catalog.

### Attributes

| Column | PostgreSQL Type | Prisma Type | Nullable | Default | Constraints | Description |
|--------|----------------|-------------|----------|---------|-------------|-------------|
| `id` | `UUID` | `String` | No | `gen_random_uuid()` | PK | |
| `menu_page_id` | `UUID` | `String` | No | — | FK → `menu_page.id` | |
| `type` | `menu_element_type` | `MenuElementType` | No | — | NOT NULL | `text`, `image`, `shape`, `product_card` |
| `x` | `NUMERIC(8,2)` | `Decimal` | No | `0` | NOT NULL | Position, px, relative to page canvas |
| `y` | `NUMERIC(8,2)` | `Decimal` | No | `0` | NOT NULL | Position, px |
| `width` | `NUMERIC(8,2)` | `Decimal` | No | — | NOT NULL, > 0 | |
| `height` | `NUMERIC(8,2)` | `Decimal` | No | — | NOT NULL, > 0 | |
| `rotation` | `NUMERIC(5,2)` | `Decimal` | No | `0` | NOT NULL | Degrees, -180 to 180 |
