### Content shapes (by `type`, stored in `content` jsonb)

| `type` | `content` shape |
|---|---|
| `text` | `{ "text": "Bienvenidos a..." }` |
| `image` | `{ "url": "https://...r2.../uploads/xyz.jpg" }` |
| `shape` | `{ "kind": "rectangle" \| "circle" \| "line", "fillColor": "#FF6B35" }` |
| `product_card` | `null` — all card data comes from the live `product` join, not from `content` |

### `style` shape (applies to `text`, `shape`, and per-field overrides inside `product_card`)

```json
{
  "fontFamily": "Outfit",
  "fontSize": 16,
  "fontWeight": 400,
  "color": "#1A1028",
  "backgroundColor": null,
  "borderRadius": 0,
  "borderColor": null,
  "borderWidth": 0,
